    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim and chop your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> in thirds, then cut lengthways into thin strips</p><p>Bash your <strong>cucumber</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and chop it into large, bite-sized pieces – this is your <strong>smashed cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
