    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once the pork belly has had 30 min, add the tray[s] with the chips to the oven and cook for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
