    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill each <strong>warmed bao bun</strong> with the <strong>quick-pickled carrot</strong> and top with a slice of the <strong>hoisin glazed pork</strong></p><p>Drizzle over a little of the <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>soy smashed cucumber </strong>and<strong> chips </strong>to the side with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
